{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one like I mentioned, that blockalteste who was-- because they were picked for this job because of that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once they got into the position, they knew in order for them to maintain a little higher standard-- whatever that meant-- it meant a little more food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It meant a little bit more freedom, because the kapos themselves didn't have to do any work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Their job was to hit us hard enough to see that we accomplished the task that they were given to us to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I would say most of the kapos used their sticks and used their-- their bats and whatever means they had to-- to abuse us to-- tremendously, let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were exceptions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were exceptions that they just did it when a-- when an SS man saw it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or they did it-- you could notice-- they did it only because they had no other choice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they knew that if they wouldn't do it, then-- then he would do it, and he would hit us harder.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I would say, to the largest extent, they were-- they were mean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many times.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a bricklayer for approximately, I think, about until 1944 in, I think, early spring or so, at which time there was a rumor going around between the old timers-- if I can call them like this.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like somebody being a rookie in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody-- we're talking about now, the era where the Hungarian transports used to come in already, from Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a rumor going around that they're looking for guys who will work in the-- in the Canada camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Canada, which is well known, was a name given by us to that detail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a special camp in Auschwitz .",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
